        <section class="py-12 md:py-14 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
            <div class="mb-10 md:mb-12 text-center">
                <h2 id="problem-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3 text-gradient">
                    The Critical Intelligence Gap
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
                    Strategic decision-makers still rely on slow, fragmented Earth observation. Data arrives late, sensors operate in silos, and the operational picture is incomplete when it matters most.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-7">
                <!-- Problem Card 1 -->
                <article class="glass-card p-7 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="text-rose-500 text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 font-bold">01</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Siloed Sensor Architectures</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
                        Optical systems fail at night and under cloud. SAR offers geometry but limited material identification. Cooperative tracking systems miss ‚Äúdark‚Äù and uncooperative targets.
                        <br><br>
                        <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">Impact:</span> No single, coherent operating picture.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <!-- Problem Card 2 -->
                <article class="glass-card p-7 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="text-rose-500 text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 font-bold">02</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Slow, Manual Workflows</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
                        Raw imagery is downlinked, stored, and processed on the ground. Tasking and cross-cueing are largely manual.
                        <br><br>
                        <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">Impact:</span> Latency measured in <span class="font-bold text-white">hours to days</span>, not minutes.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <!-- Problem Card 3 -->
                <article class="glass-card p-7 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="text-rose-500 text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4 font-bold">03</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Operational Risk</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
                        Limited ability to track ‚Äúdark‚Äù assets, slow Battle Damage Assessment (BDA), and gaps in situational awareness during high-tempo operations.
                        <br><br>
                        <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">Impact:</span> Elevated mission risk and slower decision cycles.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>

